,"uid":14690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"要搬地方"},{"pid":"428867c8c570cc7bb69fa69101a50c89f3d672f4","tid":1744544,"uid":236721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:59:11.000Z","msg":"應該唔好清場，變抗戰紀念館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56eef69506e74520de11d91607ee420d94ce394","tid":1744544,"uid":192062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"下個sem係poly cu上堂同慢性自殺無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf87a24b08445651ba160aeb1e85e90223cb08a","tid":1744544,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mGOysA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mGOysA.png&h=43729d75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52049ee85fc6b4026676f8a2f0517be0cc581164","tid":1744544,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt84E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=aec07570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}